   {
    "with": "Bloomberg",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Market Opening: US Futures up 0.18%. Tech sector seeing slight pressure ahead of earnings. Check your portfolio.",
    "time": "2026-05-04T05:37:23"
   },
   {
    "with": "Ellie",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Hey, hope the MBA workload isn't killing you. Call me this weekend if you have a gap. Love you.",
    "time": "2026-05-05T19:30:05"
   },
   {
    "with": "Whitaker 5",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Thinking about a quiet dinner at the club this Sunday? Or maybe just something in Greenwich? Let me know.",
    "time": "2026-05-06T20:12:05"
   },
   {
    "with": "Skadden Partner (Spoofed)",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Charles—urgent. Hearing whispers regarding the Atlas counterparty's 13D filing. We need to review the disclosure language before the morning bell. Call my cell.",
    "time": "2026-05-07T05:09:05"
   },
   {
    "with": "Janet Liu",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "The model looks slightly off on the synergies. Can you run the latest numbers through the sensitivity test before the 4:30 call tomorrow?",
    "time": "2026-05-04T21:26:48"
   },
   {
    "with": "CFO",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Just reviewed the preliminary QofE. Let's sync on the working capital adjustments tomorrow afternoon.",
    "time": "2026-05-08T21:00:34"
   },
   {
    "with": "Meg",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Maria is handling dinner. Are we still on for the museum event on Saturday?",
    "time": "2026-05-09T19:28:30"
   },
   {
    "with": "Nurse Elena (Caregiver)",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "[Incoming Call] - Charles Jr. is quite agitated today. He's asking for his mother again. Should we adjust the medication schedule?",
    "time": "2026-05-10T13:58:31"
   },
   {
    "with": "Chip & Ellie",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Hey guys! Are you both on? Let's catch up—I want to hear about the Goldman deal you mentioned, Chip.",
    "time": "2026-05-10T19:03:05"
   },
   {
    "with": "Meg",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "The new nurse for your dad is arriving at 8:00 AM. I've updated the shared calendar with her details.",
    "time": "2026-05-12T05:26:03"
   },
   {
    "with": "Whitaker 5",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Thinking of flying down to Hobe Sound this weekend to check on Dad. Does that work for everyone?",
    "time": "2026-05-12T19:27:11"
   },
   {
    "with": "Dr. Aris",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Mr. Whitaker, please call my office as soon as you are available regarding your father's recent lab results.",
    "time": "2026-05-13T08:26:12"
   },
   {
    "with": "Janet Liu",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Do you have the updated Atlas working capital projections? I want to review them before our Friday sync.",
    "time": "2026-05-13T21:17:18"
   },
   {
    "with": "Chip & Ellie",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Hey guys, just checking in. It's been a bit of a hectic week with your grandfather. Hope everything is good at Goldman and Stanford.",
    "time": "2026-05-14T19:19:53"
   },
   {
    "with": "Chip & Ellie",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Let's do our usual Sunday call at 7:00 PM. Talk then.",
    "time": "2026-05-17T19:02:25"
   },
   {
    "with": "Bloomberg",
    "direction": "from_anchor",
    "text": "MARKET ALERT: Unusual call option volume detected in [Ticker]. Significant deviation from 30-day mean.",
    "time": "2026-06-01T05:39:04"
   },
   {
    "with": "Meg",
    "direction": "from_anchor",
    "text": "Charles, please call me as soon as you're up. Your father had a bad fall and we're at the clinic now.",
    "time": "2026-06-02T03:24:56"
   },
   {
    "with": "Mrs. Gable",
